+ The Solar_Access_Adapter_File Class

++ Inheritance

* [Solar_Base::HomePage Solar_Base]

 * [Solar_Access_Adapter::HomePage Solar_Access_Adapter]

  * Solar_Access_Adapter_File

++ Overview

Class for reading access privileges from a text file.

The file format is:

0:flag 1:type 2:name 3:class 4:action 5:submit

E.g.:

<code>
deny handle * * * *
allow role sysadmin * * *
allow handle + Solar_App_Bookmarks * *
deny user boshag Solar_App_Bookmarks edit *
</code>